data.title: BMV: Licenses, Permits, & IDs: Driver's Manual
data.text:
The BMV’s Driver’s Manual contains the latest information you will need to successfully pass an operator’s knowledge examination (written test) and obtain an Indiana driver’s license. The Driver’s Manual is also a great way for anyone to review updated traffic laws and regulations.

Please note: Printed manuals are updated a maximum of one time each year and could contain outdated information. The most up-to-date version of the Indiana Driver’s Manual is in electronic format and available for download below in several different languages.
